@startuml
title Fee collection request and response
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #B8891E
  ParticipantBorderColor #8F6A16
  ParticipantFontColor white
  LifeLineBorderColor #B8891E
  ArrowColor #B8891E
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FBF3E0
skinparam noteBorderColor #B8891E

participant "Collecting party\n(scheme / processor)" as C
participant "Charged party\n(acquirer / issuer)" as P

C -> P : cafc.001 Fee Collection Initiation\n(Acqrr, TxId, TxAmts)
P -> C : cafc.002 Fee Collection Response (accepted / rejected)
note over C, P : same protected card-message envelope\nas the cain transaction messages
@enduml
